hotelDesc.overview:
Experience Modern Comfort at Ramada By Wyndham Seoul Dongdaemun

Welcome to Ramada By Wyndham Seoul Dongdaemun, a contemporary 3-star hotel located in the heart of Seoul, South Korea. Offering a perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and affordability, this hotel is an ideal choice for both business and leisure travelers. With a check-out time until 11:00 AM, guests can enjoy a leisurely morning before bidding farewell to their cozy accommodations. The hotel underwent a renovation in 2016, ensuring that all rooms and facilities are modern, stylish, and equipped with the latest amenities. Whether you're visiting Seoul for business or pleasure, Ramada By Wyndham Seoul Dongdaemun provides a comfortable and rejuvenating stay. Conveniently located just 70 minutes away from the airport, this hotel offers easy access to major transportation hubs, making it a breeze to explore the vibrant city of Seoul. Check-in begins at 03:00 PM, allowing guests ample time to settle in and start their adventure. With 197 well-appointed rooms, there is plenty of space for guests to relax and unwind after a long day of sightseeing or meetings. Ramada By Wyndham Seoul Dongdaemun was built in 2011, showcasing a modern architectural design that reflects the city's cosmopolitan vibe. The hotel's child policy is also family-friendly, as children between the ages of 2 to 3 can stay free of charge. Whether you're traveling with your little ones or enjoying a solo trip, this hotel ensures a comfortable and enjoyable experience for guests of all ages. Discover the perfect combination of comfort, convenience, and affordability at Ramada By Wyndham Seoul Dongdaemun. Book your stay today and experience the best of Seoul right at your doorstep.









Convenient Facilities at Ramada By Wyndham Seoul Dongdaemun

Experience a hassle-free stay at Ramada By Wyndham Seoul Dongdaemun with its array of convenient facilities. The hotel offers safety deposit boxes, ensuring the security of your valuable belongings throughout your stay. The friendly and knowledgeable concierge staff are always ready to assist you with any inquiries or recommendations, making your trip to Seoul a memorable one. Stay connected with complimentary Wi-Fi available in all rooms and public areas, allowing you to easily stay in touch with loved ones or catch up on work. Additionally, the hotel provides luggage storage, allowing you to explore the city without any worries about your belongings. With daily housekeeping, you can enjoy a clean and tidy room every day, ensuring a comfortable and refreshing stay.

Convenient Transport Facilities at Ramada By Wyndham Seoul Dongdaemun

Ramada By Wyndham Seoul Dongdaemun offers a range of convenient transport facilities to ensure a hassle-free stay for guests. The hotel provides a spacious car park onsite, allowing guests to easily park their vehicles upon arrival. Whether you are traveling by car or renting one during your stay, the onsite car park ensures that you have a secure and convenient place to park, giving you peace of mind throughout your visit to Seoul. With the hotel's car park, you can explore the city at your own pace and conveniently access nearby attractions and landmarks.

Luxurious Room Facilities at Ramada By Wyndham Seoul Dongdaemun

Indulge in a world of comfort and luxury at Ramada By Wyndham Seoul Dongdaemun, where every room is equipped with top-notch facilities to ensure a memorable stay. Step into your elegant sanctuary and be greeted by the refreshing blast of air conditioning, creating a cool and inviting atmosphere to unwind in after a long day of exploring the vibrant city of Seoul. Pamper yourself with the plush bathrobes provided, allowing you to relax and rejuvenate in style. Stay updated with the latest news and happenings with the complimentary daily newspaper, keeping you connected to the world outside. For a cozy night in, enjoy a wide selection of in-house movies on the television, providing endless entertainment options. Getting ready for a night out? Look your best with the convenience of a hair dryer, ensuring your locks are perfectly styled. Quench your thirst with the well-stocked mini bar, offering a variety of refreshing beverages. Catch up on your favorite shows with the satellite/cable TV, providing a range of channels to suit every preference. Keep your snacks and drinks cool and fresh with the refrigerator, perfect for storing any leftovers or late-night cravings. At Ramada By Wyndham Seoul Dongdaemun, every room is designed to provide the utmost comfort and convenience, ensuring a truly unforgettable stay.

Indulge in a Culinary Journey at Ramada By Wyndham Seoul Dongdaemun

At Ramada By Wyndham Seoul Dongdaemun, dining is an experience that goes beyond mere sustenance. With a coffee shop, restaurant, and daily housekeeping service, guests are treated to a delightful culinary journey that caters to every taste and preference. Start your day off right with a sumptuous breakfast buffet at the hotel's restaurant. Indulge in a wide array of international and local dishes, from freshly baked pastries and bread to a selection of hot and cold items, including eggs, bacon, sausages, fruits, and cereals. Savor the flavors and aromas as you sip on a steaming cup of coffee or tea, setting the perfect tone for an adventurous day of exploration in Seoul. For a quick pick-me-up or a cozy spot to relax, head to the coffee shop, where you can enjoy a variety of specialty coffees, teas, and refreshing beverages. Pair your drink with a delectable pastry or snack, handcrafted by skilled pastry chefs. Whether you're catching up with friends, working on your laptop, or simply taking a moment for yourself, the coffee shop provides a warm and inviting ambiance. With daily housekeeping service, you can rest assured that your dining experience at Ramada By Wyndham Seoul Dongdaemun is complemented by impeccable cleanliness and hygiene. The dedicated team ensures that the dining facilities are maintained to the highest standards, providing a safe and enjoyable environment for guests. At Ramada By Wyndham Seoul Dongdaemun, dining is not just a necessity, but an opportunity to indulge in a culinary journey that satisfies all your senses. From the breakfast buffet to the coffee shop, each dining facility offers a unique experience that enhances your stay in Seoul.

Explore the Diverse Room Offerings at Ramada By Wyndham Seoul Dongdaemun

At Ramada By Wyndham Seoul Dongdaemun, guests can choose from an array of thoughtfully designed room types that cater to every traveler's needs. The Superior Double Room, measuring 25 square meters, boasts a cozy atmosphere with a plush double bed, perfect for couples seeking a romantic getaway. For families or groups, the Deluxe Quad offers ample space with 39 square meters and four single beds, ensuring everyone has a comfortable place to rest after a day of exploration. Meanwhile, the Suite Double and Suite Twin, each spanning 58 square meters, provide a luxurious retreat with expansive living areas, ideal for those looking to indulge in a bit more space and comfort. For those traveling solo or seeking budget-friendly options, the Standard Double Room and Standard Twin Room, both at 17 square meters, deliver a charming yet efficient stay without compromising on quality. The Deluxe Family Twin Room and Deluxe Family Quintuple Room further enhance family travel, offering flexible bedding arrangements that cater to various group sizes. Booking any of these inviting rooms through otaA not only guarantees the best prices available but also ensures a hassle-free experience. With just a few clicks, you can secure your perfect accommodation at Ramada By Wyndham Seoul Dongdaemun, setting the stage for an unforgettable stay in the heart of Seoul.

Discover the Vibrant Neighborhood of Dongdaemun in Seoul

Welcome to Dongdaemun, a bustling neighborhood in the heart of Seoul, South Korea. Known for its vibrant energy and rich cultural heritage, Dongdaemun offers a unique blend of history, shopping, and entertainment. As you explore the streets, you'll be captivated by the mix of modern skyscrapers and traditional Korean architecture. One of the highlights of Dongdaemun is its famous market, which has been a hub of commerce for centuries. Here, you can immerse yourself in a sensory overload of sights, sounds, and smells as you browse through a vast array of clothing, accessories, and textiles. Don't forget to haggle for the best deals and try some delicious street food along the way. In addition to shopping, Dongdaemun is also home to several historical landmarks.
